持(chí)(6) 　“(of a demon etc.) seizes, possesses”#　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://取持">取持</a>(qŭ chí)(2), <a href="bword://下">下</a>(xià); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD. 6.548.*; DK. 5.211.*; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 459c27.或時，須菩提！若男子、女人爲鬼神所下，若爲所<span style="color: #8B0000">持</span>，是彼菩薩作是念：“或我受決已(←如)，……　是鬼神當用我故去。” (p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 190.1 = R. 383.18 = AAA. 767.28..<i>gṛhīta bhaved</i><i>āviṣ</i>ṭ<i>a~</i> (“seized or possessed [by a ghost]” [AsP.tr.II  229 = AsP.tr.  150]); ZQ. 498b18.所取; Zfn. 533a14 = Lk ; Kj. 570a16.所著; Xz(I). 836c20.所魅著; Xz(II). 908c29 = Xz(I) ; Sh. 651c1.所執魅; Tib.Pk. 225b5 = D. 209b7..<i>zin cing babs par gyur na</i>; </p>

