持(chí)(7) 　“bears”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 428b4.何因是識不可得<span style="color: #8B0000">持</span>？至本亦無所持，何因有識？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 13.11 = R. 26.2 = AAA. 112.6..<i>a-grāhya</i>~ (“cannot be seized” [AsP.tr.II  92 = AsP.tr.  10]); ps-ZQ. 481b11.無牢固; Zfn. 511a19.-.(?); Kj. 539b19.不著; Xz(I). 768a1.不可取; Xz(II). 869b1.不可取; Sh. 591a14.無著; Tib.Pk. 15b1 = D. 15a1..<i>gzung du ma mchis</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 428b4.何因是識不可得持？至本亦無所<span style="color: #8B0000">持</span>。何因有識？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 13.11 = R. 26.2 = AAA. 112.6..<i>anabhinirvṛtta</i>~ (“uncreated” [AsP.tr.II  92 = AsP.tr.  10]); ps-ZQ. 481b11.無生; Zfn. 511a19.要而不滅(?); Kj. 539b19.不生; Xz(I). 768a1.不可生; Xz(II). 869b2.不可生; Sh. 591a14.無生; Tib.Pk. 15b1 = D. 15a1..<i>mngon par ma grub pa</i>; </p>

