道(dào)(5) meaning?　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 442a11.色清淨，<span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>亦清淨。故言：“色清淨，<span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>亦清淨” (p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 93.23 = R. 186.15 = AAA. 407.9~10.<i>phala</i>-(<i>viśuddhi</i>~) ... <i>phala</i>-(<i>viśuddhi</i>~) (“[the purity of] the fruit ... [the purity of] the fruit” [AsP.tr.II  142 = AsP.tr.  62]); ZQ. 488b12.道……道; Zfn. 523c4 = Lk ; Kj. 551b22.果……果; Xz(I). 802a5 = Kj ; Xz(II). 885b6 = Kj ; Sh. 616a27 = Kj ; Tib.Pk. 112b3 = D. 105a1..<i>’bras bu ... ’bras bu</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 442b14.須菩提言：“我者清淨，<span style="color: #8B0000">道</span>亦清淨。天中天！” (p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 94.22 = R. 189.4 = AAA. 412.2..<i>phala</i>- (“fruit, result, consequence”); ZQ. 488b23.道; Zfn. 524a1.道; Kj. 551c15.果; Xz(I). 802b12.果; Xz(II). 885c1.果; Sh. 616b28.果; Tib.Pk. 114a4 = D. 106a6..<i>’bras bu</i>; </p>

