梵波産天(fàn bō chăn tiān;)(b(r)jam- pa srian:)>(QYS. bjwɒm- puâ ṣăn:)　　(<i>Brahmapārṣadya</i> Heaven)　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://梵波利産天">梵波利産天</a>(fàn bō lì chăn tiān); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 435a11.梵天上諸天人索佛道者──梵迦夷天、梵弗還天、<span style="color: #8B0000">梵</span><span style="color: #8B0000">波</span><span style="color: #8B0000">産</span>(←𤸱)<span style="color: #8B0000">天</span>、………、阿迦貳吒天等天上諸天人皆往到彼所，問訊，聽受般若波羅蜜。作禮遶竟已，各自去。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at AS. 44.1 = R. 87.11 =  AAA. 256.16.; not found at  ZQ. 485a11.; Zfn. 517a7.梵波産天; Kj. 544c11.梵衆天; not found at  Xz(I). 780b5.; not found at  Xz(II). 876c6.; not found at  Sh. 600c15.; not found at Tib.Pk. 52b2 =  D. 49b5.; </p>

