更
更(gēng)(1) 　“suffers (hardships, punishments)” especially 　“is reborn to (a lower existence)”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD. 1.526a(14).更=受(論衡 etc.); Hu 2002 : 144(安世高譯), GHY  64(2004, No.3): 81(道行般若經 etc.); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 441b9.用是斷法罪故，死入大泥犁中。若干百千歳、若干億千萬歳，當<span style="color: #8B0000">更</span>(FS.受)若干泥犁(<i>v.ll.</i>犂, 黎)中，具受諸毒，痛不可言。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 90.22 = R. 180.6 = AAA. 396.9..<i>upapatsyante</i> (“will be reborn”); not found at  ZQ. 488a8.; Zfn. 523a5..受; not found at  Kj. 550c16.; not found at  Xz(I). 800c12.; not found at  Xz(II). 884b23.; not found at  Sh. 615a25.; Tib.Pk. 109a5 = D. 101b6..<i>ltung bar ’gyur ro</i>; </p>

