過上(guò shàng)　“exceeds, surpasses”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://過…上去">過…上去</a>(guò ... shàng qù), <a href="bword://過出">過出</a>(guò chū), <a href="bword://極過…上去">極過…上去</a>(jí guò ... shàng qù), <a href="bword://出…上去">出…上去</a>(chū ... shàng qù), <a href="bword://出…去">出…去</a>(chū ... qù); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at HD.  10.955.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 428a7.摩訶衍於天上天下人中正(<i>v.l.</i>政)<span style="color: #8B0000">過</span><span style="color: #8B0000">上</span>，無有與等者。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 12.16 = R. 24.6 = AAA. 106.8..<i>abhibhavat</i>~ (“surpassing [the world]” [AsP.tr.II  91 = AsP.tr.  9]); ps-ZQ.481a20.王(諸世間)，出上; Zfn. 510c24.極過上; Kj. 539a24.勝出; Xz(I). 767b14.超; Xz(II). 868c27.勝; Sh. 590c5.爲最勝; Tib.Pk. 14a6 = D. 13b7..<i>zil gyis mnan nas</i>; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 462b18.菩薩、摩訶薩爲悉等行，諸阿羅漢、諸辟支佛所不能及。有徳之人所行道是彼極<span style="color: #8B0000">過</span><span style="color: #8B0000">上</span>。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 199.11 = R. 401.3 = AAA. 791.13..abhibhavati (“surpasses” [AsP.tr.II  238 = AsP.tr.  160]); ZQ. 499c6.所不及; Zfn. 535b14.所不及…(是彼)極過去; Kj. 572a7.勝; Xz(I). 840c1.勝; Xz(II). 910c25.勝; Sh. 654c19.不雜(聲聞縁覺行); Tib.Pk. 236a4 = D. 219a4..<i>zil gyis gnon te</i>; </p>

