還(hái)　“also, in addition to that”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD.10.1249a(6)(後漢書), Gao Yuhua 2007 : 158f.(論衡, 中本起經, 六度集經 etc.); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 459b17.菩薩、摩訶薩夢中在極高虚空中坐，爲比丘僧説經。<span style="color: #8B0000">還</span>自見七尺光，自在所變化，於餘處所，作爲如佛，説經。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 188.19 = R. 381.5 = AAA. 764.22..<i>ca</i> (“and”); ZQ. 498a.-2 = Lk ; Zfn. 532c9 = Lk ; not found at  Kj. 569c26.; not found at  Xz(I). 836a29.; not found at  Xz(II). 908b27.; Sh. 651a18.及(見自身放大光明); Tib.Pk. 224a2 = D. 208a7..<i>dang</i>; </p>

