好長(hăo cháng)　“fine and long (silk scroll)”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at HD.  4.286.; Hu 2002 : 295(道行般若經); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 478b4.書具經，正字頭角所。持時，學時，當諦授與菩薩、摩訶薩，與<span style="color: #8B0000">好</span><span style="color: #8B0000">長</span>素卷，善書，令經上下句相得。書時，當得好筆，書好素上。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at  AS. ; <span class="xr">cf. AS. 260.17f.= R. 528.3f.= AAA. 990.2f.mahāpustake pravyaktapravyaktair akṣaraiḥ sulikhitāṃ kṛtvā (“it has been well written, in very distinct letters, in a great book” [AsP.tr.II  299 = AsP.tr.  224]); ; </span>not found at  ZQ. 508b4.; not found at  Zfn. ; not found at  Kj. ; not found at  Xz(I). ; not found at  Xz(II). ; not found at  Sh. ; not found at  Tib. ; </p>

