何其(hé qí)　“why”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD. 1.1229a(詩經 etc.); GHX  204a(詩經 etc.), Wang Ying 2006 : 36(敦煌變文); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 472b18.是時釋提桓因來下化作婆羅門，問薩陀波倫言：“善男子！<span style="color: #8B0000">何</span><span style="color: #8B0000">其</span>勤苦乃爾乎？用何等故宛轉啼哭？” (p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 245.16 = R. 496.19 = AAA. 946.6..<i>kiṃ</i>(“Why [do you, son of good family, stand there dejected, pining away and shedding tears]?” [AsP.tr.II  285 = AsP.tr.  209]); ZQ. 504c26.將欲何(求勤苦乃爾)？用何等故(宛轉哭)乎？; not found at  Zfn. ; Kj. 582b11.何故; not found at  Xz(I). ; not found at  Xz(II). ; Sh. 671a22.何故; Tib.Pk. 293a6 = D. 269a7..<i>ci nyes</i>; </p>

