解止
解止(jiě zhǐ)　“rests, takes rest”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD. 10.1363b(周禮鄭玄注、三國志); <span class="xr">cf.  HD.10.1362a(18). 解 = 止; ; </span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 476c17.譬如阿迦膩吒天上天人所止觀殿，光耀悉照天上，端正姝好。……　其天人本作功徳所致。用於此間布施故，得生其上，在殿舍中<span style="color: #8B0000">解</span><span style="color: #8B0000">止</span>。用是故，其人得宮觀。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at  AS. ; ZQ. 507b15.(第舍中)止; not found at  Zfn. ; not found at  Kj. ; not found at  Xz(I). ; not found at  Xz(II). ; not found at  Sh. ; not found at  Tib. ; </p>

