金華(jīn huā)　　(name of a buddha)　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 458a18.是恒(←怛)竭優婆夷，却後當來世──名星宿劫，是中有佛名<span style="color: #8B0000">金</span><span style="color: #8B0000">華</span>佛。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 181.3 = R. 366.9 = AAA. 745.1..<i>Suvarṇapuṣpa</i>; ZQ. 497a26.金花; Zfn. 531a27.金華; Kj. 568b16.金花; Xz(I). 833c3.金花; Xz(II). 906c11.金花; Sh. 648c5.金華; Tib.Pk. 215b5 = D. 200b2..<i>gSer gyi me tog</i>; </p>

金縷
金縷(jīn lǚ)　“gold thread”　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD. 11.1189a(鹽鐵論 etc.); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 473b3.薩陀波倫菩薩及五百女人聞是，大歡欣踊躍無極，倶往至般若波羅蜜臺所，持雜華、雜香散般若波羅蜜上。持<span style="color: #8B0000">金</span><span style="color: #8B0000">縷</span>(←鏤)織成雜衣，中有持衣散上者，中有持衣作幟(←織)者，中有持衣搨(←榻)壁者，中有持衣布地(←施)者。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at AS. 250.23 = R. 508.1 =  AAA. 956.16.; ZQ. 505b8.金縷(織成雜衣); not found at  Zfn. ; not found at  Kj. 583c10.; not found at  Xz(I). ; not found at  Xz(II). ; not found at  Sh. 673a28.; not found at Tib.Pk. 299b6 =  D. 274b7.; </p>

