盡處(jìn chù)　“a limit, bound”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://盡處時">盡處時</a>(jìn chù shí), <a href="bword://極處">極處</a>(jí chù); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at HD.  7.1456.; </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 451a2.色、痛痒、思想、生死、識邊幅了不可得，無有<span style="color: #8B0000">盡</span><span style="color: #8B0000">處</span>。諸法邊幅了不可得，無有盡處。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 139.11f.= R. 279.16f.= AAA. 573.6f..asaṃkhyeya~ ... asaṃkhyeya~ (“incalculable”); ZQ. 492b12.无(←亦)盡處; not found at  Zfn. ; Kj. 559b15.-.(?); Xz(I). 818b7.無數量; Xz(II). 895c18.無數量; Sh. 633a1.不可數……不可數; Tib.Pk. 167a8 = D. 155a5..grangs med pa ... grangs med pa; </p>

