如是(rú shì)(2) 　“such being the case; if so”#　<p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">HD. 4.273b(*[禮記 etc.]); </p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 449c8.怛薩阿竭，用人故，因般若波羅蜜，知：“欲得是者，致是,”　悉知。………　<span style="color: #8B0000">如</span><span style="color: #8B0000">是</span>，須菩提！怛薩阿竭，云何知：“欲得是者，因致是”？(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">AS. 133.12 = R. 269.4 = AAA. 554.19..<i>tatra</i> (“in this connection”); not found at  ZQ. 491c10.; not found at  Zfn. ; not found at  Kj. 558a29.; not found at  Xz(I). 816b14.; not found at  Xz(II). 893c3.; not found at  Sh. 631a-9.; Tib.Pk. 159b8 = D. 148b2..<i>de la</i>; </p>

