如所從(rú suŏ cóng)　“whence, from what place”　<span class="xr">Cf. <a href="bword://所從">所從</a>(suŏ cóng); </span><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at HD.  4.273.; <span class="xr">cf. Liu Kaihua 2008 : 135; ; </span></p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-2em;">Lk. 449c1.其心者，不可以眼見<span style="color: #8B0000">如</span><span style="color: #8B0000">所</span><span style="color: #8B0000">從</span>來。(p)</p><p style="margin-left:3em; text-indent:-1em;">not found at AS. 133.2 = R. 268.12 =  AAA. 553.22.; not found at  ZQ. 491c5.; not found at  Zfn. ; not found at  Kj. 558a25.; not found at  Xz(I). 816a29.; not found at  Xz(II). 893b26.; not found at  Sh. 630c28.; not found at Tib.Pk. 159b1 =  D. 148a4.; </p>

